# Force LF on checkout for all text files, on every platform. The builder
# suite byte-compares golden fixtures against generator output (LF), and the
# answer-sheet digest is recomputed from checked-out bytes — a CRLF checkout
# (e.g. core.autocrlf=true on Windows) breaks both. Binary files are
# auto-detected and left untouched.
* text=auto eol=lf
